<http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4324.1.3>
    dc:creator "Marin, Ivan" ;
    dc:date "2017" ;
    dc:title "Athanas alpheusophilus sp. nov. (Decapoda: Alpheidae) - a new Alpheus - associated shrimp from the Russian coast of the Sea of Japan" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.997053>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.997055>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.997057>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.997061>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.997059>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.997065>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.997063> .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.997053>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Athanas alpheusophillus sp. nov., Vitjaz, Posjeta Bay, the Sea of Japan, general view of paratype female (a) and holotype male (ZMMU Ma 5839) (b)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/997053/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.997055>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Athanas alpheusophillus sp. nov., Vitjaz, Posjeta Bay, the Sea of Japan, paratypes (a, d, e – g — ovigerous female; b, c — male): a, b — front of carapace, dorsal view; c, d — front of carapace, lateral view; e — distal abdominal segments and telson, lateral view; f — telson; g — exopod of uropods." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/997055/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.997057>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Athanas alpheusophillus sp. nov., Vitjaz, Posjeta Bay, the Sea of Japan, paratypes (a, c, d — ovigerous female; b, e — male): a, b — antennula; c, e — pereiopods I (chelipeds); d — distal propodus and chela of pereiopod I." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/997057/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.997061>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Athanas alpheusophillus sp. nov., Vitjaz, Posjeta Bay, the Sea of Japan, paratype male, major pereiopod I: a — general view of pereiopod I; b — distal segments of pereiopod I; c, d — distal propodus and fingers of pereiopod I, different views." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/997061/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.997059>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Athanas alpheusophillus sp. nov., Vitjaz, Posjeta Bay, the Sea of Japan, paratypes (a – c — male; d, e — female): a, b — minor pereiopod I; c — distal propodus and fingers of pereiopod I; d — pereiopod II; e — pereiopod III." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/997059/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.997065>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. The map of records of representatives of the genus Athanas Leach, 1814 in the Sea of Japan and adjacent area. Empty sign indicates the type locality of the species." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/997065/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.997063>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Athanas alpheusophillus sp. nov., Vitjaz, Posjeta Bay, the Sea of Japan, alive coloration of female paratype (a, b) and male holotype (ZMMU Ma 5839) (c)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/997063/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

